{"tid":1410192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係元朗巴士佬，我而家好撚急尿！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T00:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:37:01.000Z","uid":141675,"like":3354,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"3c96cea8fa719ff29d18b7f98d4f2f0d5ae1dd75","tid":1410192,"uid":141675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"我屌曬你地老母！平時行一個鐘嘅車程，我依家仲未行到一半啊屌你！<br />\n<br />\n好撚急好撚急好撚急好撚急尿！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過唔！緊！要！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家仲比後面啲鹹魚屌撚晒鬼！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過都唔！緊！要！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我宣佈！你哋塞元朗博愛失得好成功！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"ce0ba5c8691b1813dcf52b284e801e2898d04660","tid":1410192,"uid":99001,"like":533,"dislike":2,"score":531,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:06.000Z","msg":"如果俾人插可以咁對答<br />\n➡️阻住我返工<br />\n❌粗口<br />\n⭕️我都好想返工啊<br />\n➡️阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n❌阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n⭕️支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n➡️你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n⭕️係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n⭕️係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n⭕️唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n⭕️林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n⭕️林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n➡️本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n⭕️請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n⭕️其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n⭕️你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會😂<br />\n➡️成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n⭕️今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n⭕️如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n➡️粗口<br />\n❌粗口回應<br />\n⭕️嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅😱<br />\n⭕️嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n⭕️你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n⭕️我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n⭕️我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n⭕️車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"7c4e5048064bd3959be2fd41e89fd484dc5d9bb4","tid":1410192,"uid":117509,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b876068c8ce299be282420f6dc09a626dc13f22f","tid":1410192,"uid":50901,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:28.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<br />\n有冇樽..."},{"pid":"5640b5d189cbcb4eded7ae92538c7a4ed1f809d7","tid":1410192,"uid":108571,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:56:09.000Z","msg":"一陣落車去個廁所啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打"},{"pid":"6c4ea5d5c3c492f9d93991ab7c520184610d86f6","tid":1410192,"uid":250391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:56:09.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋"},{"pid":"34bfc8521db64f8872c3c64b3c3fdf7f6a2fc5cd","tid":1410192,"uid":53524,"like":126,"dislike":1,"score":125,"quote":{"pid":"b876068c8ce299be282420f6dc09a626dc13f22f","tid":1410192,"uid":50901,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:55:28.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<br />\n有冇樽..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"車長位有cam<br />\n下世小心d"},{"pid":"69766ff5880bfebfab0a5a904b1664b1f7b6a526","tid":1410192,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9248ebcb1fb526dac6f05c7a53690865e71179c1","tid":1410192,"uid":264324,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕鐵好撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗去屯門"},{"pid":"d4453ff23007a2c9428942fdf94206037ac14154","tid":1410192,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8046c9db505554326c8ad6e9a8bd65ddf9cdae6","tid":1410192,"uid":269428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:01:51.000Z","msg":"多謝曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a89781c9d41e1edf9e697d4acfc290b71faf68","tid":1410192,"uid":204835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"去廁所先啦，有排塞架"},{"pid":"cd099a048888924e0d54f9233f5a7a18d9dfc2c8","tid":1410192,"uid":266289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66pgXos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66pgXos.png&h=8ac89dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9q4mP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9q4mP7.png&h=efab8691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLFsjBR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLFsjBR.png&h=fb9bb273&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dj1o3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dj1o3w.png&h=59ad9c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fe5754b878dc0866a8551d3dfacd596d273817c","tid":1410192,"uid":226955,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"喺堵塞交通呢件事上面，大家要避免陷入群眾鬥群眾嘅陷阱，可能之後開始會有（犬儒/ 廢老/ 五毛）會吹風話示威者今次真係擾到民，鬧示威者喺度搞三搞四，但係請大家諗深一層，係啲乜嘢原因令到班示威者要咁樣做？<br />\n<br />\n歸根究底係政府冇回應五大訴求呀，警察開槍射頭，虐打手無寸鐵示威者，放任埋黑社會周街打人放煙花，警察仲要同黑社會有講有笑呀，催淚彈放題、開槍打頭、唔比食藥，已經有好幾個義士暈低咗未醒返，又有少女比黑警除曬底褲，將少女私處暴露喺眾人面前，如此劣行同當年日本皇軍有乜嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可，大家如果要指責，請向政府指責，因為政府冇回應到五大訴求，責任在於政府，而唔係好似呢幅漫畫「某文化」咁，反而指責為人民向奴隸主抗爭嘅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saa7Rku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsaa7Rku.png&h=58898183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b0d7f5c76cce0aeb097b6ad65f0914f231ef439","tid":1410192,"uid":153422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2301518ff103576a176a950e449c0825a7a5438b","tid":1410192,"uid":134421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:24:17.000Z","msg":"係錦上路停左半個鐘冇郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油"},{"pid":"416248087f7f7a555a6f52050bfd075a56ed3ccf","tid":1410192,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b69a75e71008942134e759dd403ad2f2aa66dc8","tid":1410192,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270be5da9f137f5bea7388c135031f590ab40daf","tid":1410192,"uid":129733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"同乘客講聲落車路邊搞掂"},{"pid":"b3eb33716a4fafca664104011be0362ee52c96c9","tid":1410192,"uid":144492,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"落車屙啦Ching<br />\n幫手塞多兩塞"},{"pid":"ebc0443165c087efb8d440da95f5f76dd500c6cb","tid":1410192,"uid":180606,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"有經驗既司機，會有膠樽備用，你明的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ca22e150b499029f6bd04a1c95ba3d9533286f","tid":1410192,"uid":50801,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"被乘客嘈多兩野就會身體不適，到時記得call 